title: Ohio Green Party Announces State Electoral Conference (Green Party of Ohio)
text: ( Source : Green Party of Ohio ) Columbus OH : (10-21-15) The Ohio Green Party will be hosting a Statewide Electoral Conference on the 14th of November, 2015 from 1PM to 4PM . The purpose of the conference is to recruit and support candidates
